                    Our Accessibility Commitments
                </h3>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                    <li style="padding: var(--space-3) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle); display: flex; align-items: start; gap: var(--space-3);">
